    # MuZero - DeepMind's Universal Learning Algorithm
    
    **MuZero** (pronounced "mu-zero") is a groundbreaking AI algorithm developed by DeepMind, announced in 2019.
    
    ## What Makes MuZero Special
    
    Unlike its predecessors (AlphaGo, AlphaZero), MuZero learns **without** being given the rules of the game:
    
    | Algorithm | Requires Rules? | Requires Human Data? |
    |-----------|-----------------|---------------------|
    | AlphaGo | ✅ Yes | ✅ Yes |
    | AlphaZero | ✅ Yes | ❌ No |
    | **MuZero** | ❌ No | ❌ No |
    
    ## Architecture: The "Hidden State" Model
    
    ```
    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │                    INPUT                            │
    │              (Observation/Observations)             │
    └───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘
                            ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │   Representation    │  ← Learns hidden state
                │      Network (s)    │     from observations
                └───────────┬─────────┘
                            ▼
        ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
        │              SEARCH (MCTS)                   │
        │                                              │
        │  ┌─────┐   ┌─────┐   ┌─────┐   ┌─────┐      │
        │  │ s_t │──▶│ s_t+1│──▶│ s_t+2│──▶│  ... │  │
        │  └──┬──┘   └──┬──┘   └──┬──┘   └──┬──┘      │
        │     │         │         │         │          │
        │  ┌──┴──┐   ┌──┴──┘   ┌──┴──┐   ┌──┴──┐      │
        │  │Value│   │Value│   │Value│   │Value│      │
        │  │V(s) │   │V(s) │   │V(s) │   │V(s) │      │
        │  └─────┘   └─────┘   └─────┘   └─────┘      │
        │     │         │         │                    │
        │  ┌──┴──┐   ┌──┴──┐   ┌──┴──┐                │
        │  │Policy│   │Policy│   │Policy│              │
        │  │π(s) │   │π(s) │   │π(s) │              │
        │  └─────┘   └─────┘   └─────┘                │
        └──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │       OUTPUT        │
                │  (Action + Value)   │
                └─────────────────────┘
    ```
    
    ## Three Core Networks
    
    | Network | Function | Output |
