    |-----------|-------------|
    | **Agent Loop** | Observation → Reasoning → Action cycle with context maintenance |
    | **Tool Integration Layer** | File system ops, shell execution, search, extensible tools |
    | **Context Management** | Conversation history, workspace state, token-aware management |
